Gary is attempting to invent a female Viagra and manages to change three women into "zombies" 10 minutes from the end of the film for a 3 minute Nerf fight scene against cheerleaders. The zombies wore zero zombie make-up and couldn't act. The film consists mostly of sex scenes that show everything but the penetration. Very heavy into oral. Neither a zombie or horror film. Oh, and tons of male rear and female topless nudity (IMDB suggests that it ought to be a little more full-frontal, but edited versions are part for the course with Amazon).
